    "body": "Block time can't be fixed in proof-of-work, instead the follow a [poisson distribution](https://ethresear.ch/t/deep-dive-into-current-pow-difficulty-adjustment-algorithm-and-a-possible-alternative/5267). To target a different time, you would need to modify the difficulty adjustment algorithm.\r\n\r\nPlease note however, that as of geth `v1.12.0` we no longer support private proof-of-work chains.",
